    "description": "Join the EaseMyTrip family as a E-commerce Executive in Thane. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout EaseMyTrip:\nEaseMyTrip is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Thane, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with EaseMyTrip!",
